file.name: openapi-with-nested-objects.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Bakery
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  /employee-salaries:
    get:
      summary: Index method
      description: 'phpunit test string'
      tags:
        - Employee Salaries
      operationId: 'employeesalaries:index'
      parameters:
        - name: page
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
          deprecated: false
          allowEmptyValue: false
        - name: limit
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
          deprecated: false
          allowEmptyValue: false
        - name: sort
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
          deprecated: false
          allowEmptyValue: false
        - name: direction
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
          deprecated: false
          allowEmptyValue: false
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
      deprecated: false
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
  schemas:
    Place:
      description: 'Country object'
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        type:
          type: string
          example: 'countries'
        attributes:
          type: object
          properties:
            yitzo_country_code:
              type: string
              example: 'ES'
            is_active:
              type: boolean
              example: true
        relationships:
          type: object
          properties:
            description:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CountryDescription'
    CountryDescription:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        description:
          type: string
          example: 'a description'
security:
  - BearerAuth: []
